<?xml version="1.0" encoding="UTF-8"?><song><title>THE WONDERFUL STORY</title>
<lyrics>[V1]
 1. Mihing Hukdampa mak leh lopi,
 Thusim ngaihnawp a um na e!
 Migilo dinga Thipa thu chuh-
 Gen ingting, gen zel zel ingka.

[V2]
 Aw, thusim mak, thusim mak tak chuh!
 A kigen kha laka hawihpen;
 Lopi takin vel gen ka,
 Thusim mak tak mai chuh,
 A mel hawihna ka muh tieng leh.

[V3]
 2. Lopina mun apat A hung a,
 A thisan lul A hung pie tai;
 Kumsawt tatna chuh A hung siem tai,
 Ei Hukdampa A lopi ngei!

[V4]
 3. A zahngaihna luipi banga luong,
 A hehpih teh theihloh manbei;
 A lungsietna kumsawt a kiting,
 Kei nasan ei hung hukhing tai.</lyrics>
<hymn_number>251</hymn_number>
</song>